1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:02,140
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:02,140 --> 00:00:03,580
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,580 --> 00:00:05,180
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:07,450 --> 00:00:09,310
If this continues, President Kim...

5
00:00:10,080 --> 00:00:12,480
and Park Min Jun
will take over Adele Group.

6
00:00:14,190 --> 00:00:15,250
For you,

7
00:00:16,520 --> 00:00:18,220
that wouldn't be such a bad thing,
would it?

8
00:00:20,230 --> 00:00:22,230
If it's Park Min Jun
instead of my father...

9
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:25,460
Then I guess that means...

10
00:00:26,630 --> 00:00:28,070
I'll be of no use to you anymore.

11
00:00:30,140 --> 00:00:31,140
I...

12
00:00:32,740 --> 00:00:33,740
Hey, Chloe.

13
00:00:36,270 --> 00:00:37,780
The intel team found something.

14
00:00:39,180 --> 00:00:41,280
Apparently, they found it
while tracking Manager Kang.

15
00:00:41,750 --> 00:00:44,820
It seems Oh Jung Ran is the one
who kidnapped Chairman Park.

16
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:50,050
Did my mother really do this?

17
00:00:51,420 --> 00:00:54,030
All the evidence points to it.

18
00:00:55,030 --> 00:00:56,460
And it seems
she has another plan, too.

19
00:00:57,430 --> 00:00:58,630
Another plan?

20
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:02,470
Manager Kang went
to a notary's office?

21
00:01:03,470 --> 00:01:05,140
According to our intel,

22
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:09,570
it seems he made contact
a few hours ago.

23
00:01:10,210 --> 00:01:12,440
Was there something
he needed notarized?

24
00:01:12,980 --> 00:01:13,980
My guess is...

25
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:17,350
he was drawing up
a power of attorney.

26
00:01:18,250 --> 00:01:20,150
So, you mean Oh Jung Ran...

27
00:01:20,450 --> 00:01:22,350
can now act with all
of Chairman Park's authority?

28
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:28,960
(Adele Group)

29
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,900
(Power of Delegation
for Acting Duties)

30
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:40,340
If Ms. Oh comes back
with the power of attorney...

31
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:44,380
Would that work in our favor?

32
00:01:44,380 --> 00:01:45,410
Absolutely.

33
00:01:47,010 --> 00:01:49,780
Because she'll name her son
as the successor.

34
00:01:58,990 --> 00:02:00,230
We have to stop Oh Jung Ran...

35
00:02:00,690 --> 00:02:02,760
before she returns
with the power of attorney.

36
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:06,930
But the situation isn't
in our favor.

37
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:10,570
Manager Kang, who was always loyal
to Chairman Park,

38
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:14,270
is now working for Oh Jung Ran.

39
00:02:16,980 --> 00:02:18,440
Do you know where Mr. Kang is?

40
00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:20,280
We're looking for him, too.

41
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:24,520
All we know is that
he stopped by a notary's office.

42
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:28,590
I'll have my people
track down the whereabouts...

43
00:02:29,490 --> 00:02:31,990
of Manager Kang and Oh Jung Ran.

44
00:02:33,020 --> 00:02:34,630
They've gone into hiding
intentionally,

45
00:02:35,130 --> 00:02:36,830
so it'll take some time.

46
00:02:38,260 --> 00:02:40,470
Then I can't just sit back
and do nothing.

47
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:44,240
I'll set a trap
to force Oh Jung Ran's hand.

48
00:02:49,570 --> 00:02:51,340
Oh Jung Ran has power of attorney?

49
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,380
So that was her goal all along.

50
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:58,250
What about my father? Is he okay?

51
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:01,520
We don't know his exact condition.

52
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:03,420
Then we have to rescue him
right now.

53
00:03:04,660 --> 00:03:05,660
Secretary Jung,

54
00:03:05,660 --> 00:03:07,990
call an emergency board meeting
for tomorrow.

55
00:03:08,390 --> 00:03:10,630
Announce the agenda is
about emergency management rights.

56
00:03:11,060 --> 00:03:12,830
And make sure the press hears
all about it.

57
00:03:13,530 --> 00:03:14,530
Yes, ma'am.

58
00:03:14,670 --> 00:03:16,940
You're prioritizing control
over finding Father?

59
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:20,740
Are you really as power-hungry
as Hyun Jun said?

60
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:23,880
If Oh Jung Ran has
power of attorney,

61
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:27,580
she won't be able to stand by
and let me take over the group.

62
00:03:28,250 --> 00:03:30,680
That'll get her to attend
the emergency board meeting...

63
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:31,920
with the document in hand.

64
00:03:32,820 --> 00:03:35,750
The emergency board meeting
is a trap?

65
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,320
Exactly.

66
00:03:37,590 --> 00:03:40,660
The meeting is the bait I'll use
to catch Oh Jung Ran.

67
00:03:49,570 --> 00:03:52,200
- Where's Manager Kang?
- He's locked up tight next door.

68
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,070
Just because he says
he'll do as he's told,

69
00:03:56,810 --> 00:03:58,580
don't let your guard down.
Keep a close eye on him.

70
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:03,110
You can get stabbed in the back
by someone you trust,

71
00:04:05,820 --> 00:04:07,490
just like you betrayed me.

72
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:14,290
The more I think about it,
Kim Myung Hui is just ruthless.

73
00:04:14,990 --> 00:04:18,530
She knew Hyun Jun's secret,
but instead of simply exposing it,

74
00:04:20,260 --> 00:04:21,730
she arranged for me...

75
00:04:22,730 --> 00:04:24,770
to be betrayed by both you
and Park Tae Ho.

76
00:04:26,970 --> 00:04:28,110
I'm sorry, Jung Ran.

77
00:04:30,170 --> 00:04:32,080
I was just trying to do
what was best for our Hyun Jun.

78
00:04:32,580 --> 00:04:33,650
"Our" Hyun Jun?

79
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:37,680
I told you over and over again
to watch your mouth,

80
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:41,420
and now Kim Myung Hui knows.
It's all your fault.

81
00:04:44,860 --> 00:04:47,160
Do you realize how careful I've been
to avoid Park Tae Ho's suspicions?

82
00:04:48,130 --> 00:04:49,230
A DNA test?

83
00:04:50,030 --> 00:04:51,900
I could've faked the results
100 times over.

84
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:55,170
You should've let me handle it.

85
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,670
Instead, you let Kim Myung Hui
use you to betray me?

86
00:04:58,940 --> 00:05:02,340
My goal was to stop you, Jung Ran.

87
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,780
I couldn't let you hurt anyone else.

88
00:05:04,780 --> 00:05:05,780
And?

89
00:05:06,740 --> 00:05:09,350
Park Tae Ho almost killed me.
Do you realize that?

90
00:05:15,550 --> 00:05:17,890
The only reason you're still alive
is thanks to Park Tae Ho.

91
00:05:19,260 --> 00:05:22,360
If you hadn't come to warn me
that he planned to kill me,

92
00:05:22,590 --> 00:05:24,300
I would've killed you already.

93
00:05:25,900 --> 00:05:28,830
- Jung Ran!
- So shut it and do what I say.

94
00:05:29,570 --> 00:05:33,440
I'm sick of excuses about Hyun Jun
and your pathetic apologies.

95
00:05:33,710 --> 00:05:34,810
You know what?

96
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:37,340
If Chairman Park
hadn't threatened your life,

97
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:40,210
I never would've helped you
go this far.

98
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:45,820
So promise me this is the last time.

99
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:48,520
Promise me that once your position
and Hyun Jun's are secure,

100
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:50,120
you'll never do this again.

101
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:55,490
For Hyun Jun's sake,
you have to stop hurting people.

102
00:06:09,310 --> 00:06:11,710
(Adele Group,
Notice of emergency board meeting)

103
00:06:14,010 --> 00:06:17,350
After telling everyone
I'd be divorced and thrown out,

104
00:06:17,950 --> 00:06:20,020
she's calling
an emergency meeting tomorrow?

105
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,550
That's Kim Myung Hui for you.

106
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:26,760
She's ruthless and efficient.

107
00:06:27,020 --> 00:06:28,190
Is that from Director Seo?

108
00:06:29,030 --> 00:06:30,190
They're holding a board meeting?

109
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:32,300
Yes.

110
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:36,270
If you want out, now's your chance.

111
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:39,470
If not, call Director Seo
and tell him the plan.

112
00:06:42,770 --> 00:06:44,410
I'll contact Director Seo.

113
00:06:52,850 --> 00:06:55,050
It's about time
we made our move, honey.

114
00:06:57,220 --> 00:07:00,320
Want to know why I spared your life?

115
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:02,330
You're about to find out.

116
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:12,670
(Adele Group,
Notice of emergency board meeting)

117
00:07:14,410 --> 00:07:16,040
An emergency board meeting?

118
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:19,780
President Kim is trying
to take control of the company.

119
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:23,350
We must find your mother and prepare
before the board meeting.

120
00:07:23,410 --> 00:07:26,820
Is there a way to reach your mother
or Driver Song privately?

121
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:32,690
- Director Seo?
- Through Director Seo?

122
00:07:39,100 --> 00:07:42,170
I've checked all the routes
around the meeting room,

123
00:07:42,230 --> 00:07:44,800
and I'll have men posted
at every entrance.

124
00:07:45,770 --> 00:07:48,970
If Hyun Jun's mother shows up,
we'll grab her immediately.

125
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:02,720
Here's the list of directors
attending tomorrow's board meeting.

126
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:05,290
They've all confirmed
their attendance.

127
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:08,290
If things go well,

128
00:08:09,030 --> 00:08:11,300
you'll gain control
of the company, Ms. Kim.

129
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:13,100
But if they don't,

130
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:16,470
Oh Jung Ran will take control
with power of attorney.

131
00:08:22,510 --> 00:08:24,780
First, let's track
Director Seo's movements...

132
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:27,780
and see whether he shows up
at the emergency board meeting.

133
00:08:30,650 --> 00:08:35,220
Ms. Oh kidnapped the chairman
and has his power of attorney?

134
00:08:36,190 --> 00:08:38,260
If Oh Jung Ran can't be stopped,

135
00:08:38,890 --> 00:08:41,260
the company
and Min Jun's place as successor...

136
00:08:41,260 --> 00:08:42,630
will both go down the drain.

137
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:52,200
It's obvious...

138
00:08:52,770 --> 00:08:54,840
those two are on Ms. Oh's side.

139
00:08:57,280 --> 00:09:00,140
Then they could know
what she's planning.

140
00:09:04,550 --> 00:09:06,220
If I can figure that out,

141
00:09:07,490 --> 00:09:10,350
even President Kim Myung Hui
won't be able to ignore me.

142
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,690
Director Seo.

143
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:19,500
You and my mother have been allies
for over ten years.

144
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:23,270
My mother would've checked
what's going on with the company.

145
00:09:25,540 --> 00:09:27,440
You're the only one
she would've contacted.

146
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:32,680
You're secretly in touch with her,
aren't you?

147
00:09:34,650 --> 00:09:35,910
Well, that's...

148
00:09:36,010 --> 00:09:37,180
I'm...

149
00:09:39,820 --> 00:09:41,350
Ms. Oh's son.

150
00:09:43,090 --> 00:09:45,090
Whatever she's doing,

151
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:49,090
it's supposedly for my sake.

152
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:54,000
I need to know what's going on
if I'm going to help.

153
00:09:56,770 --> 00:09:57,770
Actually,

154
00:09:58,700 --> 00:10:01,110
I did receive a call
from your mother.

155
00:10:01,940 --> 00:10:03,870
Does that mean
she's coming to the board meeting?

156
00:10:04,210 --> 00:10:08,150
Yes. She said she's bringing
the power of attorney.

157
00:10:08,310 --> 00:10:09,410
Power of attorney?

158
00:10:09,650 --> 00:10:11,020
Then what about the chairman?

159
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:15,150
She said she's hiding him
somewhere secluded.

160
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,390
So...

161
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:25,160
Where exactly is this place?

162
00:10:27,130 --> 00:10:28,600
Director Seo!

163
00:10:30,740 --> 00:10:32,400
It's a facility
that recently closed.

164
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:35,470
Eunbaek Nursing Home.

165
00:10:47,180 --> 00:10:48,220
A nursing home.

166
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:50,960
Is that where she's hiding
the chairman?

167
00:10:55,530 --> 00:10:57,830
I'm sure of it.
He's in Eunbaek Nursing Home.

168
00:10:58,130 --> 00:11:00,330
It's a secluded place
that recently shut down.

169
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:03,270
Park Hyun Jun and Chloe are
on their way there now.

170
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:04,800
I'll go.

171
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,570
No, it's too dangerous.

172
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:10,810
You just had your accident,
so wait here.

173
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:13,540
Ms. Choi, please stay
by Min Jun's side for me.

174
00:11:13,810 --> 00:11:16,050
You have to keep him safe.

175
00:11:16,410 --> 00:11:17,680
Got it. Don't worry.

176
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:18,880
Mother.

177
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:20,790
I'll be fine. Let's go.

178
00:11:24,190 --> 00:11:27,890
Didn't you hear your mom?
We can't risk you getting hurt too.

179
00:11:28,090 --> 00:11:29,960
But I can't just let
my mom go alone.

180
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:34,200
I'll be fine. You stay here.
I'll be back.

181
00:11:35,930 --> 00:11:38,070
Park Min Jun!

182
00:11:43,410 --> 00:11:44,710
(Eunbaek Nursing Home)

183
00:11:44,780 --> 00:11:45,780
Hang on.

184
00:11:48,850 --> 00:11:52,380
Patient rooms are on floors 3 to 7.
The VIP rooms are on 6 and 7.

185
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:55,150
Okay, then let's start
with the seventh floor.

186
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:16,010
Nothing. Let's go.

187
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:19,880
Nothing.

188
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:23,080
Father! Father...

189
00:12:28,290 --> 00:12:31,290
(Eunbaek Nursing Home)

190
00:12:35,130 --> 00:12:36,560
(Floor Information)

191
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,630
Why don't we search
from the top down?

192
00:12:40,300 --> 00:12:42,670
No, from the bottom up.

193
00:12:43,370 --> 00:12:45,370
They'd have kept him on
a lower floor in case they needed...

194
00:12:45,370 --> 00:12:46,740
to make a quick escape.

195
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,210
Good point.

196
00:12:48,870 --> 00:12:50,140
Let's check the lower floors first.

197
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,280
Looks like no one's here.

198
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:02,820
I see more rooms up ahead.
Let's check that area.

199
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:04,520
Sure, let's go.

200
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:12,800
Help me. Somebody help.
Get me out of here!

201
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:14,570
That way.

202
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:23,110
Help me. Somebody help.

203
00:13:23,170 --> 00:13:25,140
Get me out of here!

204
00:13:25,140 --> 00:13:26,210
Wait.

205
00:13:28,510 --> 00:13:31,780
What's wrong?
That sounds like Chairman Park.

206
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:33,580
This is...

207
00:13:34,690 --> 00:13:36,290
Something feels off.

208
00:13:37,820 --> 00:13:40,560
Help me. Somebody help.

209
00:13:40,990 --> 00:13:42,890
Get me out of here!

210
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:45,330
Help me. Please.

211
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:47,500
Please!

212
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:48,530
Something's...

213
00:13:49,070 --> 00:13:50,070
not right.

214
00:13:51,740 --> 00:13:56,510
Hyun Jun. No!
No, let me go! Hyun Jun!

215
00:13:56,570 --> 00:13:58,510
No!

216
00:13:58,710 --> 00:14:00,710
Hyun Jun!

217
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:12,420
Mother!

218
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:14,860
Min Jun, no.

219
00:14:15,130 --> 00:14:18,760
What are you doing here?
I told you it was too dangerous.

220
00:14:18,830 --> 00:14:21,070
I couldn't let you
face danger alone.

221
00:14:23,770 --> 00:14:24,770
Min Jun!

222
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:28,440
- Min Jun!
- Sir!

223
00:14:29,810 --> 00:14:33,410
Min Jun, are you okay? Min Jun!

224
00:14:36,950 --> 00:14:38,620
Hyun Jun, are you okay?

225
00:14:40,050 --> 00:14:41,050
What about you?

226
00:14:42,020 --> 00:14:43,020
Are you okay?

227
00:14:45,490 --> 00:14:47,590
Yes, I'm fine.

228
00:14:58,940 --> 00:15:00,040
How could you...

229
00:15:00,300 --> 00:15:01,370
Mom!

230
00:15:03,970 --> 00:15:06,440
Are you locking us in here?

231
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:11,720
This isn't imprisonment.
It's for your own protection.

232
00:15:12,150 --> 00:15:14,220
Stay here
until I've taken care of things.

233
00:15:16,350 --> 00:15:19,820
You two getting involved
would just complicate things,

234
00:15:20,390 --> 00:15:21,960
so I'm keeping you away for now.

235
00:15:22,690 --> 00:15:24,830
There's also a chance
Kim Myung Hui...

236
00:15:25,130 --> 00:15:26,600
might expose your secret.

237
00:15:28,430 --> 00:15:31,240
Just stay locked in here
for one night.

238
00:15:33,140 --> 00:15:35,470
What are you planning
that would make you go this far?

239
00:15:36,370 --> 00:15:39,080
What about Father?
What did you do to him?

240
00:15:39,910 --> 00:15:41,910
Just how low have you sunk?

241
00:15:42,950 --> 00:15:45,350
I'm not sinking.
I'm fighting to stay afloat.

242
00:15:46,420 --> 00:15:48,720
I'm just doing everything I can
to survive.

243
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:52,620
Why does your "best"
always make me suffer?

244
00:15:54,830 --> 00:15:57,900
Was kidnapping Father for power
of attorney also for my sake?

245
00:15:59,800 --> 00:16:02,670
So if I want Adele,
I have to accept all this ugliness?

246
00:16:02,830 --> 00:16:03,830
That's right.

247
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:06,070
There's no such thing
as a free lunch.

248
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:11,740
I'll handle all the dirty work.
All you have to do is endure it.

249
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:16,880
I'll even let you two get married
like you want,

250
00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:18,950
so just wait.

251
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:47,010
- Hey.
- Hey!

252
00:16:47,010 --> 00:16:48,180
- Open the door.
- Hey!

253
00:16:48,180 --> 00:16:49,250
This is a kidnapping!

254
00:16:49,250 --> 00:16:51,520
- Hey, open the door.
- Hey!

255
00:16:54,890 --> 00:16:57,860
They took all our phones.
We're completely trapped.

256
00:16:58,160 --> 00:17:00,420
She planned this meticulously
and lured us in.

257
00:17:00,760 --> 00:17:02,490
I bet it's because
of tomorrow's board meeting.

258
00:17:03,460 --> 00:17:06,800
Oh Jung Ran made her move
to stop us from interfering.

259
00:17:08,270 --> 00:17:11,140
She could've figured out
we were setting a trap for her.

260
00:17:11,800 --> 00:17:13,300
Don't worry too much.

261
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:17,640
If she uses the power of attorney
to kick us out at the board meeting,

262
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:21,480
we still have an ace up our sleeve.

263
00:17:23,980 --> 00:17:26,280
You're going to use
Hyun Jun's secret?

264
00:17:28,290 --> 00:17:29,290
We have to.

265
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:31,920
It's our final trump card,

266
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:36,130
and you must be the one
to lead Adele Group, Min Jun.

267
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:44,300
I won't let Oh Jung Ran get her way.

268
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:46,100
Never.

269
00:17:51,780 --> 00:17:54,550
What on earth
is your mother thinking?

270
00:17:55,510 --> 00:17:59,380
If she wanted to use the power of
attorney, she wouldn't lock us up.

271
00:18:01,850 --> 00:18:04,960
What could she possibly be planning
for the board meeting?

272
00:18:14,470 --> 00:18:17,400
You must be confused by this too.

273
00:18:18,300 --> 00:18:19,300
No.

274
00:18:21,070 --> 00:18:22,270
I'm disappointed.

275
00:18:26,380 --> 00:18:27,480
My mom...

276
00:18:29,180 --> 00:18:32,180
is an even worse person
than I ever imagined.

277
00:18:35,090 --> 00:18:37,620
She killed the woman
she used to serve,

278
00:18:38,690 --> 00:18:40,390
targeted Min Jun,

279
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:43,590
took my father hostage, and now...

280
00:18:47,930 --> 00:18:49,700
she's lured us here to trap us.

281
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:55,010
It's horrifying to think...

282
00:18:56,910 --> 00:18:58,510
that I'm the son
of a woman like that.

283
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:03,680
And she says all of this is
for my sake,

284
00:19:07,850 --> 00:19:10,220
to make me the successor.

285
00:19:12,760 --> 00:19:14,160
But it's suffocating to know...

286
00:19:17,490 --> 00:19:19,500
that getting Adele means
I can't even stop...

287
00:19:20,330 --> 00:19:21,430
my own mother.

288
00:19:27,470 --> 00:19:28,670
I'm sorry, Hyun Jun.

289
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:30,540
It's my fault.

290
00:19:32,710 --> 00:19:33,710
No.

291
00:19:35,180 --> 00:19:36,410
That's not what I meant.

292
00:19:40,620 --> 00:19:43,090
My father pushed you toward revenge,

293
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,690
and my mother turned my life
into a mess.

294
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:51,190
Why did I have to be born their son?

295
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:55,300
That's what terrifies
and disgusts me.

296
00:20:00,170 --> 00:20:01,170
So...

297
00:20:02,740 --> 00:20:04,710
can you still marry someone like me?

298
00:20:07,210 --> 00:20:08,580
Or is your revenge the reason...

299
00:20:09,910 --> 00:20:11,250
you're still putting up...

300
00:20:13,950 --> 00:20:15,820
with someone as disgusting as me?

301
00:20:22,930 --> 00:20:24,290
You asked me earlier...

302
00:20:26,060 --> 00:20:27,100
whether I minded...

303
00:20:27,460 --> 00:20:30,200
President Kim and Min Jun
taking over Adele Group.

304
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:34,500
I mind.

305
00:20:35,540 --> 00:20:39,380
I have no intention of backing down,
no matter what.

306
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:44,110
I'm going to be the one
to clear my father's name.

307
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:47,820
President Kim and Min Jun.

308
00:20:48,820 --> 00:20:51,250
If they get in my way,
they'll become my enemies.

309
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:53,960
I knew that going in.

310
00:20:54,490 --> 00:20:55,560
And only you,

311
00:20:57,130 --> 00:20:58,830
the son of Park Tae Ho
and Oh Jung Ran,

312
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,500
can help me do that.

313
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:08,540
So, having you by my side...

314
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,810
is actually a relief.

315
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:20,750
The Baek Jin Ju effect
is really something else.

316
00:21:21,790 --> 00:21:22,950
Even in a situation like this,

317
00:21:24,390 --> 00:21:27,260
you still manage
to make me feel happy.

318
00:21:36,830 --> 00:21:39,640
Why is she still at work this late,
and why isn't she picking up?

319
00:21:41,140 --> 00:21:43,240
I hope everything's all right.

320
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:50,180
Jung Yoon Jung, pick up, will you?
Seriously.

321
00:21:51,250 --> 00:21:52,380
Is something wrong?

322
00:21:53,050 --> 00:21:55,220
You've been fidgeting and staring
at your phone this whole time.

323
00:21:55,950 --> 00:21:57,790
Well, I can't get in touch
with my sister.

324
00:21:59,020 --> 00:22:00,520
This has never happened before.

325
00:22:00,520 --> 00:22:03,030
Come on, don't worry so much.

326
00:22:03,530 --> 00:22:06,130
She seems capable
of taking care of herself.

327
00:22:07,430 --> 00:22:09,500
Maybe she's just trying
to avoid your nagging.

328
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:10,830
My nagging?

329
00:22:11,900 --> 00:22:15,070
Look, you might not get it
since you're an only child, Na Yeon,

330
00:22:15,470 --> 00:22:18,110
but this is just
how real siblings show they care.

331
00:22:18,310 --> 00:22:22,610
In case some weirdo hits on her
or she gets into trouble,

332
00:22:23,080 --> 00:22:26,550
I'm always watching her like a hawk
and nagging her to be careful.

333
00:22:26,650 --> 00:22:29,590
Wow, what a doting little brother.

334
00:22:40,300 --> 00:22:42,100
You're Chloe's father?

335
00:22:42,100 --> 00:22:43,170
That's right.

336
00:22:43,530 --> 00:22:45,200
I haven't been able
to reach Chloe, Park Hyun Jun,

337
00:22:45,600 --> 00:22:48,240
Ms. Kim, or Park Min Jun.
Since none of them are answering,

338
00:22:48,510 --> 00:22:49,640
I came all the way here.

339
00:22:49,910 --> 00:22:53,410
Has anyone from the family
come home yet?

340
00:22:54,110 --> 00:22:56,410
No one has returned home.

341
00:22:59,320 --> 00:23:02,090
Just as I suspected.
Something must have happened.

342
00:23:03,150 --> 00:23:05,860
I need to go to the police
and file a report immediately.

343
00:23:21,170 --> 00:23:22,640
Sir...

344
00:23:24,210 --> 00:23:27,540
Manager Kang, Driver Song,
help the chairman get settled.

345
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:29,680
- Yes, ma'am.
- Got it.

346
00:23:40,560 --> 00:23:41,560
You there.

347
00:23:43,460 --> 00:23:45,400
You're the one
who is always with Chloe.

348
00:23:48,470 --> 00:23:49,530
I'm her father.

349
00:23:50,570 --> 00:23:53,640
I couldn't reach her,
so I came here.

350
00:23:54,570 --> 00:23:55,970
If you can't tell me where she is,

351
00:23:56,770 --> 00:23:58,480
I'm going straight to the police.

352
00:24:00,040 --> 00:24:03,350
Chloe is with my son, Hyun Jun.

353
00:24:03,780 --> 00:24:06,550
What? Then why can't I reach them?

354
00:24:07,620 --> 00:24:10,790
What are the two of them
doing together this late?

355
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:13,990
You can discuss the details
in the morning.

356
00:24:14,290 --> 00:24:17,190
They'll be back safely by then,
so leave the police out of it.

357
00:24:18,230 --> 00:24:19,500
If you blow this out of proportion,

358
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:22,100
it won't do either of us any good.

359
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:23,600
What?

360
00:24:31,370 --> 00:24:33,380
Ms. Oh, please explain...

361
00:24:52,060 --> 00:24:55,070
Manager Kang,
handle the remaining details.

362
00:24:55,530 --> 00:24:56,530
Yes, ma'am.

363
00:25:10,450 --> 00:25:12,980
What have you done to the chairman?

364
00:25:15,390 --> 00:25:18,720
You're still here,
even after all this?

365
00:25:19,290 --> 00:25:22,790
After running your mouth
about kicking me out,

366
00:25:23,260 --> 00:25:24,360
you still dare show your face here?

367
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:28,100
Hey, wait.
Why are you acting like this?

368
00:25:28,930 --> 00:25:33,300
Mrs. Ok was going to keep quiet.
I made her do it.

369
00:25:33,370 --> 00:25:37,210
It's my fault,
so don't take it out on her.

370
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:42,050
For Hyun Jun's sake,
let's not cross any more lines.

371
00:25:43,080 --> 00:25:44,950
A traitor like you has no right
to lecture me!

372
00:25:47,220 --> 00:25:50,250
I'm going to teach you a lesson
you'll never forget.

373
00:25:50,650 --> 00:25:51,660
No...

374
00:26:06,040 --> 00:26:09,110
Whatever.
You're not worth the effort.

375
00:26:10,940 --> 00:26:13,110
I'm the one calling the shots
at Adele now,

376
00:26:13,610 --> 00:26:14,980
so pack your bags and go.

377
00:26:15,910 --> 00:26:17,610
If word gets out about
what happened here...

378
00:26:17,610 --> 00:26:18,720
and rumors start spreading,

379
00:26:19,620 --> 00:26:22,720
you'll pay with your life.
Understand?

380
00:26:24,220 --> 00:26:25,920
Mrs. Ok, you need to leave. Now.

381
00:26:26,660 --> 00:26:29,260
Nothing good will come
of you staying here.

382
00:26:39,040 --> 00:26:41,670
Come on. Out you go.

383
00:26:55,420 --> 00:26:58,190
Getting him his dose on time
is a real chore.

384
00:27:07,400 --> 00:27:08,400
Well?

385
00:27:08,730 --> 00:27:10,970
Feels better to be back home,
doesn't it?

386
00:27:12,770 --> 00:27:16,240
Soon, I'll even let you see
your precious Kim Myung Hui.

387
00:27:17,710 --> 00:27:21,610
I wonder whether
she'll choose you or Adele.

388
00:27:23,880 --> 00:27:26,350
I'm curious to see
what she'll decide.

389
00:27:36,790 --> 00:27:38,360
The board meeting is about to start,

390
00:27:38,860 --> 00:27:40,530
so where's President Kim?

391
00:27:40,800 --> 00:27:42,570
I can't reach Min Jun either.

392
00:27:44,900 --> 00:27:46,170
Did something happen?

393
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:48,470
Should I call the police?

394
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:52,080
What?

395
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:54,880
Manager Kang,
what are you doing here?

396
00:27:55,050 --> 00:27:57,780
Weren't you kidnapped by Ms. Oh
with the chairman?

397
00:27:58,420 --> 00:28:02,690
Then is the chairman coming back?
Will he attend the board meeting?

398
00:28:04,220 --> 00:28:05,320
What about Min Jun?

399
00:28:05,420 --> 00:28:07,920
What happened
to President Kim and Min Jun?

400
00:28:08,990 --> 00:28:10,830
Please, just say something.

401
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:15,770
Today's...

402
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,740
board meeting has been canceled.

403
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:23,270
President Kim and Director Park
will also be back soon.

404
00:28:28,310 --> 00:28:29,880
The board meeting has been canceled?

405
00:28:30,850 --> 00:28:32,920
What about control of the company
and Min Jun?

406
00:28:34,420 --> 00:28:36,420
What in the world is going on?

407
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,400
You're free to go now.

408
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:53,870
Is the board meeting already over?

409
00:28:54,040 --> 00:28:56,440
The board meeting has been canceled.

410
00:28:56,870 --> 00:28:57,870
Canceled?

411
00:28:58,440 --> 00:29:01,980
You're telling me Oh Jung Ran
gave up her shot at taking over?

412
00:29:02,580 --> 00:29:05,120
Did my father cancel it,
by any chance?

413
00:29:05,450 --> 00:29:06,980
You can hear the rest at home.

414
00:29:07,050 --> 00:29:09,450
Only Ms. Kim and the director
are expected back.

415
00:29:10,890 --> 00:29:13,760
This is a family matter, Ms. Jung.
You can go home now.

416
00:29:14,390 --> 00:29:16,930
No. I'm going with them.

417
00:29:18,090 --> 00:29:20,760
We'll be fine. Don't worry too much.

418
00:29:20,760 --> 00:29:22,100
But...

419
00:29:22,100 --> 00:29:25,140
I've got her back, so don't worry.

420
00:29:37,580 --> 00:29:39,450
She's waiting for you inside.

421
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:44,290
I'll go in first.

422
00:30:01,800 --> 00:30:05,040
Honey, your precious
Kim Myung Hui is here.

423
00:30:07,740 --> 00:30:09,180
Did you kidnap the chairman...

424
00:30:10,380 --> 00:30:12,320
and put him into a coma?

425
00:30:13,520 --> 00:30:14,520
Beats me.

426
00:30:15,620 --> 00:30:19,560
We met in the gallery vault,
and then he suddenly collapsed.

427
00:30:19,820 --> 00:30:21,760
I took him to the hospital.

428
00:30:21,760 --> 00:30:24,090
Fearing the worst,
he gave me power of attorney.

429
00:30:24,190 --> 00:30:27,560
And a short while later,
he slipped into a coma.

430
00:30:28,130 --> 00:30:30,330
So that's how
you're going to spin this?

431
00:30:31,470 --> 00:30:35,770
I have the medical records prepared,
and Manager Kang is my witness,

432
00:30:36,670 --> 00:30:37,910
so who's going to say otherwise?

433
00:30:38,510 --> 00:30:40,780
The only reason
you'd keep the chairman alive...

434
00:30:41,410 --> 00:30:42,980
must be because
of the power of attorney.

435
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:45,350
So why did you cancel
the board meeting?

436
00:30:47,080 --> 00:30:48,350
You could've kicked us out...

437
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:51,550
and taken over Adele.
So why didn't you?

438
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:58,260
If I had used the power of attorney
at the board meeting,

439
00:30:58,530 --> 00:31:01,730
you would've revealed
Hyun Jun's secret to everyone.

440
00:31:02,500 --> 00:31:04,400
A battle between
the power of attorney...

441
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:05,470
and the DNA test results...

442
00:31:05,970 --> 00:31:07,440
would be a lose-lose situation
for both of us.

443
00:31:07,600 --> 00:31:10,610
So what are you proposing?

444
00:31:12,780 --> 00:31:15,710
You and me. The two of us.

445
00:31:16,750 --> 00:31:19,620
For 30 years, we've fought
to take control of Adele...

446
00:31:20,120 --> 00:31:21,380
from Park Tae Ho.

447
00:31:23,420 --> 00:31:27,890
And for me, those 30 years
feel like a complete waste.

448
00:31:31,260 --> 00:31:34,200
How about we finally put an end
to this tiresome fight?

449
00:31:35,830 --> 00:31:37,700
Park Tae Ho is out of commission,

450
00:31:38,700 --> 00:31:41,540
and Adele is more than big enough
for both of us.

451
00:31:42,540 --> 00:31:43,540
What?

452
00:31:44,810 --> 00:31:48,210
We'll sideline Park Tae Ho
and split Adele between us.

453
00:31:48,710 --> 00:31:52,080
We'll each take the firms we want
and split them fairly, fifty-fifty.

454
00:31:53,520 --> 00:31:57,050
If our sons each take over
a part of Adele,

455
00:31:57,850 --> 00:32:01,660
don't you think they could get along
without fighting one another?

456
00:32:03,230 --> 00:32:06,260
If I keep your son's secret buried,

457
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,730
you'll give me half of Adele?

458
00:32:09,170 --> 00:32:10,170
Well?

459
00:32:10,930 --> 00:32:13,740
It's an offer too good to refuse,
wouldn't you say?

460
00:32:49,570 --> 00:32:52,610
(Pearl in Red)

461
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:54,210
- First, I want to know...
- Father.

462
00:32:54,210 --> 00:32:55,310
- what you did to the chairman.
- Father!

463
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:57,910
Let's just say Park Tae Ho
will never wake up.

464
00:32:57,980 --> 00:32:59,150
In that case...

465
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:00,780
I have to admit, it's a good deal.

466
00:33:00,850 --> 00:33:02,090
You make my blood boil.

467
00:33:02,090 --> 00:33:05,860
The shame and disgust
you make me feel drive me insane!

468
00:33:05,920 --> 00:33:09,230
I want to use this opportunity
for everything it's worth.

469
00:33:09,330 --> 00:33:11,560
My dad's car accident
from seven years ago.

470
00:33:11,860 --> 00:33:13,660
I'm going to get the case reopened.

471
00:33:15,330 --> 00:33:17,330
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
